## 편의상 생략된 코드
예제에 앞서 가독성을 위하여 공통으로 사용되는 다음 코드들을 생략합니다. 
1. `JavaScript Library`를 Load
    ```html
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@sj-js/visnetworkman/vis-network.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@sj-js/visnetworkman/vis-networkman.min.js"></script>
    <script>
         var visnetworkman = new VisNetworkMan();
    </script>
    ```  
  
2. Node를 구성할 `Data`를 Load
    ```html
    <script>
        //1. Data
        var dataList = [
            {id: 0, label: 'START', group:0, parentId:null},
            {id: 1, label: 'Node 1', group:1, parentId:0},

            {id: 3, label: 'Node 3', group:1, parentId:0},
            {id: 4, label: 'Node 4', group:2, parentId:0},
            {id: 7, label: 'Node 7', group:3, parentId:0},
            {id: 11, label: 'Node 11', group:2, parentId:1},
            {id: 14, label: 'Node 14', group:2, parentId:1},
            {id: 15, label: 'Node 15', group:2, parentId:1},
            {id: 15, label: 'Node 15', group:2, parentId:3},
            {id: 21, label: 'Node 21', group:2, parentId:2},
            {id: 24, label: 'Node 24', group:2, parentId:2},
            {id: 25, label: 'Node 25', group:2, parentId:2}
        ];
    </script>
    ```
   
3. `<Body>`태그

## Simple
`.setup()`, `.setupExtendsOption()`을 거쳐서 `.renderWithDataList()`를 통해 Network를 간단히 표현할 수 있습니다.
- test
    *@* *!* *@*
    ```html
    <script>
        //2. Setup - VIS Network Options
        visnetworkman.setup({
            nodes: {
                shape: 'box'
            }
        });
   
        //3. Setup - VIS NetworkMan Options   
        visnetworkman.setupExtendsOption({
            nodeWhenStart: {color: {background:'#b2e2d9', border:'#19211f'}},
            edgeWhenStart: {color: {color:'#aae35f'}},
        });
   
        //4. Render
        var container = visnetworkman.renderWithDataList( dataList );
        document.body.appendChild( container );
    </script>
    ```
  
## Pointing and Selecting
마우스를 Node에 올리거나 Click하여 선택했을 때 Node와 Edge의 Style을 지정할 수 있습니다.
- test
    *@* *!* *@*
    ```html
    <script>
        //2. Setup - VIS Network Options
        visnetworkman.setup({
            nodes: {
                shape: 'star'
            }
        });
   
        //3. Setup - VIS NetworkMan Options   
        visnetworkman.setupExtendsOption({
            modePointAllSubLink: true,
            modeSelectAllSubLink: true,
            nodeWhenStart: {color: {background:'#b2e2d9', border:'#19211f'}},
            edgeWhenStart: {color: {color:'#aae35f'}},
            nodeWhenPoint: {color: {background:'#ff1559', border:'#ff1559'}},
            edgeWhenPoint: {color: {color:'#ff1559', opacity:1}},
            nodeWhenSelect: {color: {background:'#df2a20', border:'#df2a20'}},
            edgeWhenSelect: {color: {color:'#df2a20', opacity:1}},
        });
   
        //4. Render
        var container = visnetworkman.renderWithDataList( dataList );
        document.body.appendChild( container );
    </script>
    ```
  
  

## Event
Event를 통해서 `초기 각 Node별 설정` 또는 `Click`, `DoubleClick`등의 Action을 제어할 수 있습니다.
- test
    *@* *!* *@*
    ```html
    <script>
        //2. Setup - VIS Network Options
        visnetworkman.setup({
            nodes: {
                shape: 'triangleDown'
            }
        });
   
        //3. Setup - VIS NetworkMan Options   
        visnetworkman.setupExtendsOption({
            modePointAllSubLink: true,
            modeSelectAllSubLink: true,
            nodeWhenStart: {color: {background:'#b2e2d9', border:'#19211f'}},
            edgeWhenStart: {color: {color:'#aae35f'}},
            nodeWhenPoint: {color: {background:'#ff1559', border:'#ff1559'}},
            edgeWhenPoint: {color: {color:'#ff1559', opacity:1}},
            nodeWhenSelect: {color: {background:'#df2a20', border:'#df2a20'}},
            edgeWhenSelect: {color: {color:'#df2a20', opacity:1}},
            funcEventSetupNode:function(node){
               return;
               switch (node.type){
                   case 1: break; //Product
                   //REF: https://icon-icons.com/ko/%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EC%BD%98/%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%ED%8C%80/57998
                   case 2: node.image = { unselected:'data:image/png;base64,',}; break; //Group
                   //REF: https://icon-icons.com/ko/%EC%95%84%EC%9D%B4%EC%BD%98/xmag-%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89-%EC%B0%BE%EC%95%84-%EC%88%98%EC%B6%9C-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0/5422
                   case 3: node.image = { unselected:'data:image/png;base64,'}; break; //Search
                   default: console.log('[SETUP] Unknown Node: ', node); break;
               }
            },
            funcEventSetupEdge:function(edge){
               //TODO: Something
               if (edge.toNode){
                   // edge.arrows = {to: {enabled:true, scaleFactor:0.1}};
                   if (edge.toNode.relevance){
                       var maxWidth = 40, minWidth = 5;
                       edge.width = Math.max(Math.min(Math.floor(edge.toNode.relevance * maxWidth), maxWidth), minWidth);
                       //TEST - Highlight Edge with Relevance
                       var maxOpacity = 1, minOpacity = .2;
                       if (!edge.color)
                           edge.color = {};
                       edge.color.opacity = Math.max(Math.min(edge.toNode.relevance *1.35, maxOpacity), minOpacity);
                   }
               }
            },
            funcEventClickNode:function(node){
               switch (node.type){
                   case 1: alert('product'); break; //Product
                   case 2: alert('group'); break; //Group
                   case 3: alert('search'); break; //Search
                   default: console.log('[CLICK] Unknown Node: ', node); break;
               }
            },
        });
   
        //4. Render
        var container = visnetworkman.renderWithDataList( dataList );
        document.body.appendChild( container );
    </script>
    ```
  
## Extends Panel
마우스를 올려보세요. `ExtendsPanel`의 버튼으로 즉각적으로 그래프 구성을 바꿔볼 수 있습니다.
- Test
    *@* *!* *@*
    ```html
    <script>
        //2. Setup - VIS Network Options
        visnetworkman.setup({
            nodes: {
                shape: 'hexagon'
            }
        });
   
        //3. Setup - VIS NetworkMan Options   
        visnetworkman.setupExtendsOption({
            modePointAllSubLink: true,
            modeSelectAllSubLink: true,
            nodeWhenStart: {color: {background:'#b2e2d9', border:'#19211f'}},
            edgeWhenStart: {color: {color:'#aae35f'}},
            nodeWhenPoint: {color: {background:'#ff1559', border:'#ff1559'}},
            edgeWhenPoint: {color: {color:'#ff1559', opacity:1}},
            nodeWhenSelect: {color: {background:'#df2a20', border:'#df2a20'}},
            edgeWhenSelect: {color: {color:'#df2a20', opacity:1}},
            modeExtendsPanel: true,
            modeExtendsPanelAutoHide: true,
            modeExtendsPanelSaveToLocalStorage: true,
            extendsPanelToggleDefaultIndexMap:{
                'direction':0,
                'directionMethod':0,
                'duplication':1,
                'unification':2,
                'edgeLimit':6,
            },
        });
   
        //4. Render
        var container = visnetworkman.renderWithDataList( dataList );
        document.body.appendChild( container );
    </script>
    ```
    - `modeExtendsPanelSaveToLocalStorage`을 `true`로 설정하면 눌렀던 데이터들이 LocalStorage에 저장되어 기억시킬 수 있습니다.
    - 만약 여러 그래프를 다룰 경우 `saveKey`옵션에 각각 다른 Key를 입력하여 버튼의 상태를 다르게 관리할 수도 있습니다.
